# Plugin-flattened skill symlinks created by .agents/plugins/flatten.sh
#
# These are machine-specific symlinks pointing into
# ~/.claude/plugins/cache/<marketplace>/<plugin>/<version>/skills/<name>/
# and are regenerated by a Claude Code SessionStart hook on every session.
# Never commit them — their targets are absolute paths, version-pathed, and
# different on every machine.
cc-*
